U.K. Proposes Cut for Tariffs on Solar Plants Bigger Than 50 Kilowatts

-- B y   M a r c   R o c a
-- 
2011-03-18T11:09:04Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-18/u-k-proposes-cut-for-tariffs-on-solar-plants-bigger-than-50-kilowatts.html
The U.K. government proposed cuts
for above-market rates paid for solar energy on future projects
bigger than 50 kilowatts, an e-mailed statement from the
Department of Energy and Climate Change said today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Marc Roca in London at 
